## Enable Google Sheet API and link to Glific

Go to [Google Cloud Console](https://console.cloud.google.com) and sign in with your Gsuite account.

Click on **API Service**

Click on **+ Enable APIS and Services**
Search for **Google Sheets API** in the search section select it.
Enable the **Google Sheets API** from the enable button

## Link Google Sheets API to Glific

Go to Glific >> Settings>> Google Sheets >>Tick is Active >> Paste the GOTH credentails >> Save
